{"tid":1655511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我可能係一個左膠，但係希望勇武會睇睇","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T07:14:51.000Z","uid":334389,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"07c95b65f39d507ae9ad4cdb654f3e533d228812","tid":1655511,"uid":334389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"我本身都唔會打算開連登既ac<br />\n但係見到有d嘢好想出聲<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">私了</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins>是咁的，大家都可以蒙面保護自己<br />\n被八卦藍絲影相時可以開遮<br />\n人地移開路障時 佢搬出 我地一班人搬翻入<br />\n同佢但出彈入<br />\n武力解決方法永遠留到最後plz</ins><br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以理性，盡力穩住民意<br />\n點解咁講 因為我屋企人本來都係普通港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近佢地越來越向藍發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都唔希望私了風氣過火，普通豬市民真係會驚<br />\n唔好讓自己變成PoPo 我的都要克制冷靜plz<br />\n<br />\n民意係最緊要<br />\n<br />\n我都有心理準備負皮滿滿，但係我覺得自己做左自己認為有幫助既嘢就足夠<br />\n<br />\n最後永不割蓆"},{"pid":"251a6496a8a827470b776c93ddbbe1ddc629ccfc","tid":1655511,"uid":282624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwfNVQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwfNVQj.jpg&h=e2c88fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"274572ab2f4aa0df9906a031c200969c3190b0d9","tid":1655511,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655497</a>"},{"pid":"664a53a332612a32ca7291d3116ea431ca38fdde","tid":1655511,"uid":41366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"私了？<br />\n你唔諗下d手足點樣俾人虐待"},{"pid":"6adab0b5b9d5c2a918a2856ec89668452d259260","tid":1655511,"uid":51932,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"我希望有市民被藍絲打，你第一